metadata.name: DON'T
metadata.description:
A reminder to not look - 2023  
Created from an analog collage.

Michelle's collage work explores themes such as censorship, concealment of identities, and the creation of new ones, drawing influences from classic advertising. 

Michelle has been working as an Illustrator and collage artist for the past 26 years. A graduate from The Royal College of Art, she has been at the forefront of illustration working successful in publishing, editorial and design. Clients have included the New York Times, Apple, Sky, Channel Four and the Washington Post to name a few. 

https://www.michelle-thompson.com
